individual access to our set.

701
00:39:52,766 --> 00:39:54,267
Right.

702
00:39:54,351 --> 00:39:57,437
-That's right.
-So we decided to draw straws.

703
00:39:58,772 --> 00:40:02,442
And Sports Eunseong
happened to be picked first.

704
00:40:02,526 --> 00:40:04,402
Man, Sports Eunseong is so lucky.

705
00:40:04,486 --> 00:40:07,072
We plan to invite every reporter on set

706
00:40:07,155 --> 00:40:09,491
before we finish shooting the drama,

707
00:40:09,574 --> 00:40:12,160
so we'd appreciate it
if you could wait a bit longer.

708
00:40:12,244 --> 00:40:14,329
So they were going to invite everyone.

709
00:40:14,788 --> 00:40:15,831
Yes.

710
00:40:15,914 --> 00:40:18,834
Yes, please be patient.
Meanwhile, we'll take more questions.

711
00:40:19,501 --> 00:40:20,502
The reporter in the back?

712
00:40:21,086 --> 00:40:23,713
